:'''Saul''': Yeah, well Clarence Darrow never had a client like you ask him for something... [''Saul retrieves the ricin cigarette, in a plastic bag, from his desk.''] ...like this, okay? I put my ass on the line for you. Huell too, huh? He's got fingers like hot dogs. He coulda easily bust this in two and killed everyone in the office. But do I complain? No. Beg, borrow, or steal, I am your [[w:Huckleberry Finn|Huckleberry]]. I go the extra mile. Only you never told me that kid would wind up in the hospital! You know, take that thing and get the hell out of here. You and me, we're done. 
