=== ''[[w:Confessions (Breaking Bad)|Confessions]]'' [5.11] ===

:'''[[w:Hank Schrader|Hank]]''': Mr. Pinkman. How are you today? Not so good, huh? 'Course, uh, I might be able to help you out. I wanna talk to you about your partner, Heisenberg. See, I know he's my brother-in-law, Walt.
